{"tid":422263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你今日要返工呀？窮廢撚生存就係用來供養有錢人","createTime":"2017-10-03T02:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T00:33:20.000Z","uid":40470,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1a2eef7efe8f5d042dcb85dd7d0be7140772556b","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你做一個鐘50蚊個鐘<br />\n<br />\n其實你本來可得200蚊<br />\n<br />\n但大把人un un腳望住你做<br />\n<br />\n你做得越賣力佢地就收得越多<br />\n<br />\n你勤力d佢就賺多d錢去食貴野叫正雞<br />\n<br />\n如果你條柒頭唔出力做就炒鳩你<br />\n<br />\n你唔做大把人做<br />\n<br />\n因為你廢，所以你就要窮<br />\n<br />\n合情合理<br />\n<br />\n返工啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e016f824bc2fbc253cb1ed6fd573676afa49c482","tid":422263,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:06:23.000Z","msg":"點解你要講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd0167eed2cb868dc1a8b036684f01cdff66c4f","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:08:26.000Z","msg":"你？<br />\n<br />\n50蚊個鐘人工咁下賤<br />\n<br />\n左計右計搭地鐵貴d<br />\n<br />\n但可以訓多半個鐘<br />\n<br />\n你條柒頭就搭地鐵啦<br />\n<br />\n點知壞車返到公司比老細黑你要扣左你勤工200<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5926341d97715f5dc1362054f82b56d6be641aff","tid":422263,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:10:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dce106fbfc7aad3066ecdc2a0bc9b686b3d89931","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:12:29.000Z","msg":"死磨爛磨磨到食lunch<br />\n<br />\n你條柒頭排隊食工廠區食堂<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母你得50蚊個鐘咁撚下賤？<br />\n<br />\n你又左計右計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你三餸飯好似最撚抵喎<br />\n<br />\n上次讚完個姐後生佢fuck多左d碎豆腐比你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6509481888946651450eb803924b912841c7739","tid":422263,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:13:42.000Z","msg":"資本主義就係咁嫁啦，勞工實際生產所有的價值。<br />\n<br />\n但大部分勞工，只可以得到價值中的一小部分作為報酬。<br />\n<br />\n其他的剩餘價值，就全部歸少數人擁有，然後佢哋就可以攞呢D錢為所欲為。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1184ed3449d27274147bb111265ced8689e90266","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:19:32.000Z","msg":"呀姐你今日件衫好sharp呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFuck多件豆仆比...<br />\n<br />\n你未講完已經用個飯盒掉鳩你同下個柒頭fuck緊飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你其實返工無朋友！<br />\n<br />\n拎住個飯盒去公園戇鳩鳩獨家村食你個閪窿三餸飯<br />\n<br />\n屌你d飯未收水好似食緊廢老糊仔咁既？<br />\n<br />\n屌你d菜入面有鋼絲刷既？<br />\n<br />\n屌你個釀豆仆d魚肉咁撚惺既？<br />\n<br />\n係呀抵你死呀屌你老母因為你好撚下賤50蚊個鐘咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137bb23b434728668bb94252126fed04200c88c1","tid":422263,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:21:43.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀"},{"pid":"0d8b203bf9b1defbe6aca5e1ccd8db51ee2a0bc4","tid":422263,"uid":85880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:25:22.000Z","msg":"樓主一定係啲毒撚拎一個鐘50蚊件要比人欺凌 上黎狗吠屌人發洩 好悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f5c507d12bfa251aad86e1714cb00d1aa67002","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:26:42.000Z","msg":"叫下午茶喇柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記低唔撚好落錯單呀<br />\n<br />\n上次凍撚茶無少甜呀撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你條柒頭最多人肯同你開口講野係下午茶時段<br />\n<br />\n平時你只係一個時薪50蚊佈景人<br />\n<br />\n大把野比你重要<br />\n<br />\n因為<br />\n<br />\n一個影印機<br />\n<br />\n一個電腦<br />\n<br />\n老細用既架啡機<br />\n<br />\n死物既operation cost都比你條柒頭高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4959daa2f539635608b97de8210cbbadc55c0faa","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:36:18.000Z","msg":"無驚無險<br />\n<br />\n又到六點<br />\n<br />\n挨多個半鐘你條柒頭就可以放工喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你條撚樣時薪確實係50蚊<br />\n<br />\n但係每日要做兩三個鐘義工喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係呀鬼叫你廢呀<br />\n<br />\n公司個個都叻過你條廢物<br />\n<br />\n太子爺年少有為，因為佢爸爸係老闆<br />\n<br />\n女上司好做得野，因為26歲仲係童顏巨乳<br />\n<br />\n老屎忽德高望重，因為係老闆親戚<br />\n<br />\n門口reception時薪120唔使IT，因為吹工了得<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母呀你條撚樣時薪50，好好反省下點解你咁廢呀"},{"pid":"fdf16d9cb1fa9522326363abf9b733d3584997ae","tid":422263,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07377ad3865f75f072ac064ac442f5517d33bd58","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嘻嘻嘻<br />\n<br />\n好好笑呀好好笑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做爛做似隻雞，俾人鬧仲要開口笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n似隻雞，好好笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俾人鬧仲要笑笑口，似隻雞，好好笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你一定要做到以上既野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔做大把人做呀，比大拿拿50蚊個鐘你嫁屌你老母西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但你唔好覺得你真係雞喎<br />\n<br />\n你搵得50蚊，雞都不如呀你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371bfe342c12c8ef7d19a4cb9bfe701af4ee2ff8","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:45:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嘻嘻嘻<br />\n<br />\n好好笑呀好好笑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">死</span>做爛做似隻雞，俾人鬧仲要開口笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n似隻雞，好好笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俾人鬧仲要笑笑口，似隻雞，好好笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你一定要做到以上既野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔做大把人做呀，比大拿拿50蚊個鐘你嫁屌你老母西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但你唔好覺得你真係雞喎<br />\n<br />\n你搵得50蚊，雞都不如呀你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"edac4e6763fc59dafd9423ebc2d53f5126e5eab0","tid":422263,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:46:04.000Z","msg":"好痛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8ec57a4be1d1193fd778b034dda6433d14935c","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:56:07.000Z","msg":"嘩屌你<br />\n<br />\n你果次幾撚威猛呀<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你好撚捨得用左7份1時薪去買一盒凍𢭃奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但汽水機條柒頭唔肯出𢭃奶比你喎？<br />\n<br />\n你兜野踢鳩佢之後速逃呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你要知汽水機時薪成80嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你成世人最勇猛就係呢次以下犯上呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ef8dba49bbb1a1d6b2fc89bf96ce077f0ddb48","tid":422263,"uid":50818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:05:35.000Z","msg":"嘈撚夠未阿屌你老母<br />\n今日唔洗返工阿，ok？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0302671c23df02aaaf758103becfdf7c90d0cd1","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:17:20.000Z","msg":"50蚊柒頭要起香港生存<br />\n<br />\n首先要明白香港李氏供求學：<br />\n<br />\n李氏第一定律：（Li's first law of fate），又稱爲慣性貧窮定律，定律指出出生者父親為窮人，其必是窮人;出生者父親為富人，其必是富人。此定律確立於無外力環境影響之下。<br />\n<br />\n李氏第二定律：（Li's second law of motivation）施加於人的金錢引誘，金錢越多，人的動力越大。<br />\n<br />\n李氏第三定律：（Li's third law of supply and demand）你唔做，大撚把人做。"},{"pid":"e467336489f48a750911a8f0ba8eb0c198a1ea09","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:28:09.000Z","msg":"孫悟空好威猛呀！<br />\n<br />\n每次都打贏敵人<br />\n<br />\n你細過一定有幻想過自己係孫悟空<br />\n<br />\n但係你條柒頭每日每日長大<br />\n<br />\n每日每日長大出來社會做野<br />\n<br />\n其實你什麼都不是<br />\n<br />\n莫講話孫悟空<br />\n<br />\n柒頭比達你都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n笛子魔童都無你份<br />\n<br />\n你想講你可以做呀樂？<br />\n<br />\n不<br />\n<br />\n你只係培植人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3230046a0e64818cc2b744a123c2ef9b09cbf494","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:31:42.000Z","msg":"培植人同你好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n外型樣衰<br />\n<br />\n低學歷<br />\n<br />\n無父幹（直情老豆都無）<br />\n<br />\n起地下捐出來<br />\n<br />\n用完即棄<br />\n<br />\n最勁果下係自爆<br />\n<br />\n無限一個龜波氣功打死幾隻"},{"pid":"f1044e73604501b6964cdeb6dec8bf0dfccdec79","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"最重要係<br />\n<br />\n培植人戰鬥力50<br />\n<br />\n同你一樣，時薪50既柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n李生，就係宇宙大王級，千億能量戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14a60234d6cd4ac5bb45b6f9eaabb2207b24401","tid":422263,"uid":815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:34:52.000Z","msg":"保安男又出嚟吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192a3ded1d6bd3a835500628d964da2852f1b900","tid":422263,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:36:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保安男又出嚟吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<br />\n<br />\n講緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea0fbdaf91b812a9e72ea90217422aacb3ea697","tid":422263,"uid":52585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:36:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f694df53db8c2dcfc871c1da767dd9d981a0a498","tid":422263,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:37:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}